Name:
* Adem Kilicci TUR disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to IOC Disciplinary Commissions desicion of January 27 2017 after a retest of his samples from the 2012 Olympics. 




Men's Middleweight - Boxing - London 2012 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     The competition was a single elimination tournament without seeding where the winner of each match   advanced to the next round. Winners of the semifinals qualified for the Gold Medal match. Both losers were awarded Bronze Medals. Event facts: Men's Middleweight competition was held at the ExCel and 28 athletes participated in the event.
